metadata.description: Indulge in the harmonious Duality Oshizushi, an artistic blend of delicate flavors and textures. Resting on a thin bed of white rice, you'll find two enticing pieces of fish, one rich tuna and one tender salmon. Adorned with a drizzle of tangy sweet sauce and Japanese chili mayo, this masterpiece is topped with vibrant orange and red Ikura, adding a burst of flavor and color to this heavenly creation.
metadata.name: Duality Oshizushi #62 #1/8
